---
title: Flow 1 - Authentication
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant W as Workers
    participant A as Access
    participant F as FastAPI

    User->>W: GET /
    W->>A: check cookie
    A-->>User: redirect to login
    User->>A: authenticate
    A-->>User: set cookie
    User->>W: GET / (with cookie)
    W->>A: validate
    A-->>W: pass
    W-->>User: serve SPA
    User->>W: GET /api/balance
    W->>F: GET /balance + secrets
    F-->>W: JSON
    W-->>User: render balance
